SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Keep it stable.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Well done.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Check your parameters.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: You better practice this.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: TT:to-slow-for-a-scramble

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: We are still on the ground. Get yourself together!

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: You struggle, you better practice hovering.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Proceed to LZ Alpha. Maximum speed. Altitude at your discretion.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: You may proceed to LZ Bravo. Keep a low profile over the river to avoid radar detection.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Next waypoint LZ Charlie. Here you have location data. Tune your IFR equipments before takeoff.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: We are late to LZ Charlie, 3 penalties.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Minimum safe altitude is 5300 feet in this area.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: It was a walk in the park, right? Return to base.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Almost home. Land on the apron, I deserve a breakfast.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Secure the aircraft. Tired? We are almost done.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Perform shutdown checklist. I wait for engines shut down, rotor stopped, dark cockpit.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Checkride complete. Excellent control and discipline. You’re qualified. Welcome to the line.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Checkride complete. Pass. Performance acceptable. Tighten it up.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Checkride complete. Pass — marginal. You meet the standard, barely. Fix the basics.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Checkride complete. Pass by tolerance only. One more mistake would have ended it.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: That’s ten. Checkride terminated. Unsatisfactory. Practice, practice, and practice.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Lieutenant. This is your aircraft. Five minutes to a stable hover. Don’t waste it.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Payerne Tower, Kilo Bravo Three Five, request start.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: TT:cleared-for-start

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Kilo Bravo

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Payerne Tower, Kilo Bravo Three Five, request takeoff.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: TT:cleared-for-takeoff

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Kilo Bravo

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: TT:radar-contact

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Kilo Bravo

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Ignore the freight terminal. Main Station is city center.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Payerne Tower, Kilo Bravo Three Five, inbound, request recovery.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: TT:proceed-direct-apron

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Kilo Bravo

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: TT:cleared-to-land

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Cleared to land, Kilo Bravo

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Timing matters, Lieutenant. Three penalties.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: You just painted us on radar. Two penalties.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Never get tired of that view… beautiful, isn’t it?

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Leg update. Fly zero three zero, eighty knots, two thousand five hundred feet. QNH two niner five one.

SimMission.DialogAction.Speaker: PILOT
SimMission.DialogAction.Text: Leg update. Fly to Bern Main Station, one hundred twenty knots, two thousand eight hundred feet. QNH two niner five one.
